{
    "data": [
        {
            "title": "特朗普稱美國很快對藥品加徵關稅 逼藥企離開中國及在美設廠",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"特朗普稱美國很快對藥品加徵關稅 逼藥企離開中國及在美設廠\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/64ea0e10524436edac77898f98159ab5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040910500424163.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">特朗普稱美國很快對藥品加徵關稅 逼藥企離開中國及在美設廠</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美國總統特朗普發表講話時表示，美國很快宣布一項重大的藥品進口關稅，以逼使藥廠離開中國，並認為一旦對藥品徵收關稅，製藥公司將在美國開設工廠，因為美國是「最大的市場」。\n\n</p>\n<p>特朗普表示，美國並不生產自己的藥品和其他改善健康的產品，而美國支付藥品的價格往往比有藥品生產的國家高出很多倍。他又強調，許多國家曾經剝削美國，現在輪到美國採取行動。\n\n</p><h2>組織籲歐盟行動減輕風險</h2>\n<p>另一方面，歐洲製藥公司在與歐洲委員會主席的會議上警告，美國關稅將加速該行業從歐洲轉向美國趨勢。製藥行業貿易游說組織EFPIA亦表示，已呼籲歐盟主席推動「迅速而根本性的行動」，以減輕向美國外流的風險。\n\n</p>\n<p>特朗普上周向全球宣布「對等關稅」時未有涉及藥品，但他表示藥品將面臨單獨的關稅。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062936/即時-財經-特朗普稱美國很快對藥品加徵關稅-逼藥企離開中國及在美設廠",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-09 10:56:13",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中環唐樓頂樓冒濃煙 消防救熄無人傷 疑神壇失火",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"消防到場救熄火警。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/db819f7292c5722abf92dc2ce6812b90/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040910465217416.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">消防到場救熄火警。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中環結志街23號，今（9日）早上9時09分，頂樓冒出濃煙，消防接獲多個報告，出動一喉一煙帽隊到場，約20分鐘將火撲熄，期間數名居民自行疏散，無人受傷。單位外牆熏黑。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184878/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防拖喉灌救。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d853e5b04c94ff44d84dda9213073662/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250409_103049437_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防拖喉灌救。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184879/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單位外牆熏黑。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/53e9ba2f2b5ca0d1e59396f06ae7737a/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250409_103049437_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單位外牆熏黑。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184880/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9b19a143c637d6738dd5e358dbce5c87/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250409_103049437_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184882/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防到場救熄火警。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0bb2f72647420042aa96656a539301f0/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250409_103049437_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防到場救熄火警。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184883/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防到場救熄火警。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1b7112d26ccc99cef7ee2cbc1d9d307b/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250409_103049437_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防到場救熄火警。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>現場為唐樓，起火是5樓頂樓單位，消防破門入屋，當時室內無人，初步估計神壇失火，並無可疑。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062935/即時-港聞-中環唐樓頂樓冒濃煙-消防救熄無人傷-疑神壇失火",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-09 10:51:31",
